Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Vendor across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - Vendor per case, aggregated by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum duration of Accepted + Wait - Vendor when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait - Vendor
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait - Vendor in variants containing both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait - Vendor when it appears after Accepted + Assigned
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Elapsed time from the start of the case until Accepted + Wait - Vendor is performed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + Wait - Vendor to be completed after its initiation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total waiting time to Accepted + Wait - Vendor when preceded by Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait - Vendor to Completed + Resolved in variants that include Completed + In Call elsewhere in the trace
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait - Vendor compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - User within the same variant patterns
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Time between Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Vendor in cases that never execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total time from case start to Accepted + Wait - Vendor in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + Wait - Vendor and Completed + Closed when Completed + In Call is absent in the trace
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
